deprecated: true
resource: BackendConfig
status: not-used-with-gateway-api
reason: >-
  GKE Gateway API deployment is the active ingress path for this project.
  BackendConfig is a GCE Ingress resource and is intentionally not applied.
notes:
  - Kept as reference for historical Ingress-based deployments only.
  - Health checks are managed via HealthCheckPolicy templates in
    infrastructure/ansible/roles/gke-deploy/templates/.
